Instead of giving up, we made a commitment to improve. We went back to the lab, carefully revisiting every ingredient, every concentration, and every feedback point. Kojic Acid is a powerful active that works wonders for many, but it’s not suitable for everyone, especially those with sensitive skin. Knowing this, we aimed to create a balanced formula, effective yet gentle.

While the journey isn’t over, we’ve made significant progress. Our updated formula pairs Kojic Acid with soothing and hydrating ingredients to brighten skin while minimizing potential irritation. It’s lightweight, non-comedogenic, and designed to help fade dark spots and even out skin tone without clogging pores.

We’re proud of how far this product has come and grateful for the trust you’ve placed in us throughout this process. Your feedback has been invaluable, and your patience has pushed us to keep striving for better.

For those who love this cream, thank you for making it a part of your skincare journey. For those for whom it didn’t work, we hear you, and we’re continuing to refine and improve.

The 2% Kojic Acid Night Cream is more than just a product, it’s a reflection of our promise to learn, grow, and deliver honest science for your skin. Thank you for being a part of this journey.
